{"id": 2132, "genre": 1000, "title": "关于公司用来考核员工表现的标准，你都见过哪些不合理之处？", "description": "啥样的 KPI 会让你对工作更有热情，或者更心如死灰？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 7195, "comment_count": 19, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180121151857HXLgPeAvwfrs18Qu.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-01-24T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 3612, "title": "关于公司用来考核员工表现的标准，你都见过哪些不合理之处？", "content": "关于公司用来考核员工表现的标准，你都见过哪些不合理之处？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 260700, "content": "拿“在朋友圈宣传公司新闻”这种表面功夫衡量员工表现", "image": "img/option/option/20180121152729vHEWoQsKPGtiyUwC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 260733, "content": "绩效和奖金都以整个部门的表现计算，全部门都一样", "image": "img/option/option/20180121225351Tk8SptNrXmbiCYo1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 260734, "content": "销售、市场能不能达标很大程度上取决于业务部门产品做咋样", "image": "img/option/option/20180121225449k4sCHwR0Fy6TidcV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 260735, "content": "没法覆盖所有工作，实际情况中有一些成果难以量化", "image": "img/option/option/20180121225656scOraKC6tEoUTLnR.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 260736, "content": "盲目要求每年业绩都有进步，不考虑大环境变化", "image": "img/option/option/20180121225709t7xT4aDgdnjZq6GW.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 260737, "content": "标准设置偏差，电商考核只看拉新用户数，不看他们有没有消费", "image": "img/option/option/201801212259238bk6iv4nSNzFmEhw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 260738, "content": "繁琐、走形式的自评、互评，浪费时间也没有区分度", "image": "img/option/option/201801212301504dtn0BqALTHCQkp1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 260739, "content": "最开始完全没有明确考核标准，只在最后公布结果", "image": "img/option/option/20180121230207n4F6KtjabBiz9Vc0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}